metadata.name: Queen of the Gas Station 1/1
metadata.description:
Limited runs on a beat up Mustang, defined by function, forged through old-fashioned expressions of ridiculous swagger. Automotive home turf. Rich immigrant histories recall dialog in motion, inanimate objects infused with paradox and paradigm. Blazing neon cromalam sneakers, socks. Decorative polychromatic botanic hues, custom mended denim patches, strawberry purse.

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing a floral yellow and blue puffy jacket with a ripped denim miniskirt, black high top sneakers, white blue hair, red lipstick, walking down Manhattan in the 2000s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
